Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.90,1:18:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,ta vẫn sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.06,1:18:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta vẫn sẽ
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.82,1:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,không hối hận
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.78,1:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,vì đã gặp cô.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.24,1:18:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Người đời sợ ta, ghét ta.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.50,1:18:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chỉ có cô...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.09,1:18:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,chỉ có cô thương ta, bảo vệ ta.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.06,1:18:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhu Cơ.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.71,1:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ẩn Nương,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.79,1:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,sau khi gặp cô,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.50,1:19:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhu Cơ.
